OL,3,CFlowers and toy left at scene where
OL,4,Cbaby girl died in fall from building
OL,6,FFlowers have been left outside a
OL,7,Fresidential property where a baby girl
OL,8,Ffell from a height and died.
OL,10,FThe Metropolitan Police said officers
OL,11,Fattended Horseferry Road in
OL,12,FWestminster, central London, after
OL,13,Freports on Saturday morning that a
OL,14,Fbaby had fallen from a height.
OL,16,FThe infant ` aged 18 days ` was
OL,17,Fpronounced dead in hospital.A 43-year-
OL,18,Fold woman arrested at the scene on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of murder was taken into
OL,20,Fpolice custody.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
