OL,3,CFlowers and toy left at scene where
OL,4,Cbaby girl died in fall from building
OL,6,FFlowers and a toy animal were left
OL,7,Fnear the Peabody Estate building on
OL,8,FSunday morning where a police cordon
OL,9,Fhad been lifted.
OL,11,FTwo forensic officers could be seen
OL,12,Fworking in a third-floor flat on
OL,13,FSaturday evening.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Alison
OL,16,FFoxwell said: "The death of an infant
OL,17,Fis always an extremely tragic
OL,18,Foccurrence, and officers are making
OL,19,Furgent inquiries around the
OL,20,Fcircumstances.
