OL,3,CFlowers and toy left at scene where
OL,4,Cbaby girl died in fall from building
OL,6,F"At this stage, we believe the
OL,7,Fincident occurred within a domestic
OL,8,Fcontext, but we are appealing for
OL,9,Fanybody with information to come
OL,10,Fforward."
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the London
OL,13,FAmbulance Service said the baby was
OL,14,Ftreated at the scene before being
OL,15,Ftaken to a major trauma centre.
